      "job_description": "About Us:\nLunad Digital Portal LLC operates www.yellowpages-uae.com, a premier listing directory in the UAE. We are looking for a talented Web Developer to join our team and contribute to our growing digital presence.\n\nJob Description:\nWe are seeking a skilled Web Developer with hands-on experience in front-end and back-end development. The ideal candidate will be proficient in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, C#, VB, and ASP.NET Core. Additionally, experience with MS SQL Server and writing SQL procedures is essential.\n\nResponsibilities:\n• Develop and maintain web applications using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, C#, and VB.\n• Build and optimize ASP.NET Core applications.\n• Design, implement, and manage MS SQL Server databases.\n• Write and optimize SQL procedures.\n• Collaborate with a team based in the UAE, working according to UAE work timings.\n• Ensure responsive design and improve overall user experience.\n• Troubleshoot and debug issues as they arise.\n• Keep up-to-date with the latest web development trends and technologies.\n• Coordinate with the team and manage tasks effectively while working remotely.\n\nRequirements:\n• Proven experience as a Web Developer.\n• Strong knowledge of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, C#, VB, and ASP.NET Core.\n• Hands-on experience with MS SQL Server and SQL procedures.\n• Familiarity with front-end frameworks and tools.\n• Ability to work independently and manage time effectively.\n• Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.\n• Own a personal laptop and a reliable internet connection.\n• Willingness to work according to UAE timings.\n• Ability to work from the office in Bangalore, Karnataka in the future, if needed.\n\nNote: Please ensure you meet all the requirements before applying. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted for an interview.\n\nLunad Digital Portal LLC is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.\n\nJob Type: Full-time\n\nPay: ₹25,000.00 - ₹30,000.00 per month\n\nSchedule:\n• Day shift\n\nEducation:\n• Bachelor's (Preferred)\n\nWork Location: Remote\n\nSpeak with the employer\n+91 9742832133\nExpected Start Date: 01/06/2024",
