      "job_description": "Job Title: Web and UI Designer & Webflow Developer (Part-time and Full-time)\n\nJob Description:\n\nWe're looking for a great web and UI designer who can not only create a fantastic design but also translate the web design to a Webflow website. Someone with a passion to understand user needs and craft beautiful UI and user experiences. Collaborate with the Product and Tech team to create a stunning website, design marketing collaterals and create engaging user experience and UI.\n\nResponsibilities:\n• Design website, marketing collateral and UI using design tools like Figma.\n• Develop and maintain a design system in Figma for maintainability as well as quick turnaround time\n• Translate Figma website design to Webflow pages.\n• Develop and Maintain a component library in Webflow for maintainability as well as quick turnaround time\n• Liaise with the Product and Tech team to understand and deliver on design brief for the Product (UX as well as UI design)\n• Liaise with the Marketing team to understand and deliver on design brief for the Product (UX as well as UI design)\n• Conduct periodic user research (qualitative as well as quantitative methods including in-depth interviews) to understand user needs and to optimize UI/UX design\n• Conduct periodic experiments (AB test etc.) to optimize design for Conversions\n\nRequirements:\n• Expert at Figma with a track record of designing and maintaining Websites and Applications including knowledge of creating and maintaining design systems.\n• Expert at Webflow with a track record of developing and maintaining Websites including deep knowledge of Webflow CMS as well as creating and maintaining a component system\n• Good knowledge and experience in implementing UX and UI best practices\n• Excellent sense of design and knowledge of contemporary design trends and aesthetic\n• Good to have knowledge of designing marketing and other collaterals\n• Ability to work in a highly agile and dynamic startup environment with good collaboration and communication skills\n• Time management and the ability to work on tight deadlines and deliver on time\n• Attention to detail and finesse\n\nAdditional Info:\n\nWe are open to people working on a Part-time or full-time basis and working remotely as well.\n\nAbout Skillcamper:\n\nSkillCamper is an online learning platform that helps upskill individuals for various roles in the field of Data Science. We emphasize on Domain expertise and problem solving and design thinking and not just technical competence. Our mission is to empower anyone who is interested in learning any skill related to Data with the knowledge and platform to master that skill in the shortest possible time at the lowest possible cost. We do this by creating an application focused curriculum and a platform that provides the most optimum learning environment based on the latest scientific research and technology.\n\nJob Type: Freelance\nContract length: 3-4 months\n\nPay: From ₹9,402.29 per month\n\nBenefits:\n• Flexible schedule\n• Work from home\n\nEducation:\n• Bachelor's (Preferred)\n\nExperience:\n• Web design: 2 years (Required)\n• Web development: 2 years (Required)\n• Figma: 2 years (Required)\n• Website Maintenance: 2 years (Required)\n\nWork Location: Remote",
